 ref‚ÜêInjectTatinVars(projectRoot folder);cfg;ref2
‚çù When a package is loaded, a namespace `TatinVars` is injected into the root of the package by Tatin.
‚çù When Cider opens a project that carries a file apl-package.json in the projects's root folder, it
‚çù injects such a namespace in the root of the project by default.\\
‚çù However, more often than not a sub-namespace of the project will eventually become the package.
‚çù In such a case you might want to have `TatinVars` in the root of the _**package**_ namespace.\\
‚çù You can achieve that by injecting a property `tatinVars` into the Cider config file (as part of
‚çù `CONFIG`) in order to specify a sub-namespace that will eventually become the package.
‚çù Cider will then inject `TatinVars` into that sub-namespace rather than the root of the project,
‚çù This allows a developer to access `TatinVars` while working on the project as if it were loaded
‚çù as a package.\\
‚çù `ref‚Üê‚éïNULL` if the project does not have a package config file and a ref to `TatinVars` otherwise.
‚çù point to a sub-namespace in the project's root.
 ref‚Üê‚éïNULL
 :If ‚éïNEXISTS folder,'/',‚éïSE._Tatin.Registry.CFG_Name

     ‚çù With Tatin 121.0 "ReadPackageConfigFile" was renamed to "GetPackageConfigFileAsNS"
     ‚çù For compatability we make sure that Cider works with both versions:
     :If 3=‚éïSE._Tatin.Registry.‚éïNC'ReadPackageConfigFile'
         cfg‚Üê‚éïSE._Tatin.Registry.ReadPackageConfigFile folder
     :Else
         cfg‚Üê‚éïSE._Tatin.Registry.GetPackageConfigFileAsNS folder
     :EndIf

     ‚éïSE._Tatin.Client.EstablishStuffInTatinVars projectRoot cfg folder
     ref‚ÜêprojectRoot.TatinVars
     :If 0<projectRoot.CiderConfig.CIDER.‚éïNC'tatinVars'
     :AndIf 0<‚â¢projectRoot.CiderConfig.CIDER.tatinVars
         :If '‚éïthis'‚â¢‚éïC projectRoot.CiderConfig.CIDER.tatinVars
             :If 9=projectRoot.‚éïNC projectRoot.CiderConfig.CIDER.tatinVars
                 ref2‚ÜêprojectRoot‚çéprojectRoot.CiderConfig.CIDER.tatinVars
                 ((‚çïref2),'.TatinVars')‚éïNS projectRoot.TatinVars
                 projectRoot.‚éïEX'TatinVars' ‚çù Policy change in 2024-07
                 ref‚Üêref2.TatinVars
             :Else
                 ‚çû‚Üê'"tatinVars" does not point to a sub-namespace in the project''s root',‚éïUCS 10
             :EndIf
